{"id": 2755, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都有哪些安慰式购物习惯？", "description": "没吃饱、睡不着、对象太狗、老板太凶……算了，逛会淘宝吧。（题图来自：iStock ©️ nuvolanevicata）", "record_count": 2264, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190122122109RTUQBfLPNAm6S34g.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-02-07T17:00:33Z", "options": [{"id": 326656, "content": "熬夜了皮肤不好 去小红书种种草买点护肤品 然后越熬越晚", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1556134}, {"id": 326658, "content": "我的恩格尔系数特别高。生气难过的时候买的东西大多是便宜企鹅不理智的。因为穷。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578378}, {"id": 326914, "content": "学期末买各科资料", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1558607}, {"id": 326659, "content": "化妆没人看也不能不买口红眼影盘", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1505323}, {"id": 326661, "content": "喝奶茶 我连做完一篇英语阅读理解都想要奖励自己一杯奶茶。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 477519}, {"id": 326662, "content": "一闲下来就买鞋", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 110}, {"id": 326663, "content": "写完这篇论文了，买点想看的书犒劳一下自己🤟🏻", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578455}, {"id": 326667, "content": "心情不好 就一个人逛商场吧 看到喜欢的就买 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1577971}, {"id": 326669, "content": "考试一定得买新笔 仿佛这样就能考好一样", "image": "img/option/option/20190209105318fCO4LGpA9kyersQN", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578479}, {"id": 326670, "content": "过年回婆婆家，一定要把和老公第一次逛的那条街走一遍，奶茶喝一遍。要不感觉这千里迢迢白回来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 585058}, {"id": 326926, "content": "默默看了一眼steam。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 335185}, {"id": 326671, "content": "心情不好 买零食吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578508}, {"id": 326672, "content": "看喜欢的品牌官网有没有上新的包，收藏。逛家居app看别人好看的家。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578300}, {"id": 326673, "content": "我就随便看看🌚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1524770}, {"id": 327185, "content": "心情不好的买买东西真的很有用 一是分散注意力二是解压买一下平时喜欢的东西有满足感", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1341767}, {"id": 326674, "content": "开心了买，不开心了也买", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1282669}, {"id": 326675, "content": "上班没衣服穿了 一定会买点", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578574}, {"id": 326676, "content": "瓷器是我的安慰剂。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578588}, {"id": 327188, "content": "嘴巴有些寂寞，买点吃的吧！\r\n你不胖，买点吃的吧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497481}, {"id": 327189, "content": "被安利安利买点实用小物品", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1581681}, {"id": 326679, "content": "心情不好买各种东西，甚至给别人买礼物，通过这样和别人说“我很好”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1253319}, {"id": 326681, "content": "心情不好了就买点东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1541069}, {"id": 326683, "content": "这类产品我有一个就不考虑其他了...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 506265}, {"id": 326684, "content": "心情不好出去吃点东西犒劳犒劳自己活着上上网", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578675}, {"id": 329757, "content": "吵架了，买个东西安慰自己，告诉自己，别人对自己不好，自己要对自己好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1595636}, {"id": 327710, "content": "买口红就是救命神药", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1577068}, {"id": 327711, "content": "以前是学习的时候先买本和笔，不开心了听晴天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1577068}, {"id": 326687, "content": "先是买一件衣服，然后就想买个背包，再来买块表，最后又买了件外套", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1470283}, {"id": 326688, "content": "想变的有气质买书买衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578296}, {"id": 326689, "content": "压力大 先买点东西压压惊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114661}, {"id": 326691, "content": "无聊买买买", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1570959}, {"id": 326692, "content": "心情不好，压抑", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578782}, {"id": 326693, "content": "好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1063107}, {"id": 326695, "content": "我就看看不买……然后就没钱了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 110005}, {"id": 326696, "content": "感觉自己好久没购物了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1405029}, {"id": 326697, "content": "买书，且看书\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1492953}, {"id": 326700, "content": "想学习了就买笔", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1574430}, {"id": 326701, "content": "买书买书买书买书买书", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578870}, {"id": 326702, "content": "考的不好就买书", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578870}, {"id": 326703, "content": "学习不在状态的时候会想要买各种收纳的东西…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578874}, {"id": 326959, "content": "睡不着就买书", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1580427}, {"id": 326704, "content": "买自己根本不会用的英雄的皮肤；（\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1427297}, {"id": 326705, "content": "买颜料，买本子，买印泥", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578881}, {"id": 326706, "content": "每月有钱买瓶香水，心满意足", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 964771}, {"id": 326707, "content": "看到好书不管能不能读懂先买下来存到书架上。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1450964}, {"id": 326710, "content": "单词背不下来，买本单词书重头在来！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578954}, {"id": 326711, "content": "做不完的工作开始前看场电影。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578954}, {"id": 326713, "content": "熬夜前的咖啡红牛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1576446}, {"id": 326715, "content": "最后一次了，买完在卸载", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578996}, {"id": 326716, "content": "打不好篮球买篮球鞋穿", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578999}]}